{"tid":516555,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中華人民國債","createTime":"2018-01-01T13:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T08:12:59.000Z","uid":18668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1098eb4a67bc149517486803cd14b3aff5e2d2bb","tid":516555,"uid":18668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"不嬲有買開支那國債<br />\n今年有無呀？<br />\n睇報紙完全無人提過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以往都係12月出<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80cceb0d84035f15400149054f1a04b68ad423c","tid":516555,"uid":18668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:04:57.000Z","msg":"有無巴打知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a95c2a8fcf7a46fdf2d2a47a3d92a04dab38626","tid":516555,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"唔係6月出左咩"},{"pid":"de3039341fa7473555357a2312dd27e76b4f9435","tid":516555,"uid":18668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171122/bkn-20171122102220992-1122_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171122%2Fbkn-20171122102220992-1122_00842_001.html&d=bThROXMWT9S%2Fy0S8rVjPEOI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=a39d8826\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171122/bkn-20171122102220992-1122_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>中國財政部公布，經國務院批准，2017年財政部在香港發行140億元人民幣國債。其中，6月22日已發行70億元，11月27日當周將再發行70億元。<br />\n<br />\n此次發行的70億元人民幣國債，將通過香港債務工具中央結算系統(CMU)面向機構投資者、國外中央銀行、地區貨幣管理當局發行，具體期限結構和發行時間將於發行前公佈。人民幣國債發行後，將在香港聯合交易所掛牌上市交易。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以我所知，應該無出，睇新聞話今年分左兩個時間出，但係都無零售國債，以前出之前會有新聞報紙講，今年完全無人講"},{"pid":"6893daea8a3e9293516712f406a311ba3bf71be9","tid":516555,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:08:29.000Z","msg":"入場費好似勁高？"},{"pid":"29776e947256f8adca801ee0f13794b98cd553f5","tid":516555,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:36:08.000Z","msg":"玩支那宝仲好啦<br />\n活期都4厘"},{"pid":"7427ea17f7489d0b6a9442a2ca8261059f10cb3e","tid":516555,"uid":119825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:47:52.000Z","msg":"搵間銀行做定期啦，有近4厘。"},{"pid":"518624430ee09ae9f27fc4790896f7ae510a869c","tid":516555,"uid":44980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"上去開個銀行戶口大把債你揀自己買"},{"pid":"42893a2173460e1c9e217f98f5cd0888ca74e0a2","tid":516555,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"華人的怨恨，除了共產黨，還有儒家的尊卑之分，怨恨無地方伸張，只能發洩落下一代或弱勢的人，大部份最後慢慢形成斯德哥爾摩症後群去同情和一代又一代去延續。<br />\n儒家沒有教導民主，而是剛剛相反教導尊權和卑賤。"}]}